projectSummary: This auditorium booking platform recently integrated an Express server and optimized frontend performance with React hooks while updating visual assets for multiple campus locations. The team is actively building administrative capabilities including analytics dashboards, calendar scheduling, and email notifications alongside ongoing interface refinements.
